==English==

===Etymology===
From [[postcard]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''postcardware''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#{{cattag|Computing}}: A software [[product]] whose author requests as payment, a postcard sent to them from the users hometown.

